20That%20is%2C%20it's%20a%20lot%20easier%20to%20come%20by%20today.%20In%201929%2C%20information%20was%20often%20already%20old%20even%20on%20the%20NYSE%20floor%20itself%2C%20let%20alone%20at%20brokerages%20around%20the%20city%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-bubble-andrew-ross-sorkin-1929-crash-book-ai-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAndrew%20Ross%20Sorkin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20CNBC%20host%20who%20recently%20published%20%26quot%3B1929%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20examines%20the%20infamous%20stock-market%20meltdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20there%20were%20so%20many%20people%20in%20the%20streets%20is%20people%20had%20gone%20down%20there%20physically%20because%20they%20wanted%20to%20see%20what%20was%20actually%20happening%20to%20their%20investments%2C%26quot%3B%20Sorkin%20said%20on%20Bloomberg's%20Odd%20Lots%20podcast.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20you%20couldn't%20call%20somebody%2C%20there%20was%20no%20app%20to%20look%20at.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20one%20example%20of%20how%20much%20the%20world%20and%20the%20stock%20market%20have%20changed%20in%20the%20last%2096%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20book%2C%20Sorkin%20mentions%20a%20number%20of%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20market%20landscape%20was%20different%20in%20the%20years%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20crash%20and%20the%20subsequent%20Great%20Depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20seven%20big%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWomen%20were%20not%20allowed%20on%20the%20trading%20floor%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227864%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22nyse%20statue%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6904f2b9599d46a4ccc13fec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224912%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBruce%20Bennett%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWomen%20weren't%20allowed%20on%20the%20NYSE%20floor%20until%201943%2C%20during%20World%20War%20II%2C%20when%20there%20was%20a%20shortage%20of%20workers.%20The%20first%20women%20to%20work%20on%20the%20floor%20were%20%26quot%3Bquote%20girls%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcarrier%20pages.%26quot%3B%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F1943%2F07%2F11%2Farchives%2Fstock-exchange-to-make-36-young-women-quote-girls-and-carrier-pages.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times%20wrote%20a%20story%20about%20it%20at%20the%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20impossible%20to%20ignore%20that%20this%20was%20a%20world%20shaped%20almost%20entirely%20by%20men%2C%26quot%3B%20Sorkin%20writes%20about%20the%20early%2020th%20century%2C%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWomen%20were%20neither%20welcomed%20on%20the%20trading%20floor%20nor%20permitted%20to%20shape%20its%20rules%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20women%20lead%20the%20entire%20exchange.%20The%20NYSE%20has%20had%20two%20women%20presidents%20since%202018%3A%20Stacey%20Cunningham%20and%20its%20current%20president%2C%20Lynn%20Martin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EYou%20could%20pay%20actors%20to%20bid%20up%20a%20stock%20on%20the%20exchange%20floor%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22robert%20downey%20jr%20jeremy%20renner%20nyse%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6904f699599d46a4ccc140b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222294%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBrad%20Barket%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOK%2C%20they%20weren't%20actors%20as%20famous%20as%20Jeremy%20Renner%20and%20Robert%20Downey%20Jr.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20really%2C%20it%20was%20perfectly%20legal%20to%20pay%20people%20posing%20as%20traders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20book%2C%20you'll%20see%20there's%20a%20guy%20named%20Mike%20Meehan%20who's%20the%20specialist%20on%20the%20floor%20for%20RCA.%20He%20used%20to%20run%20these%20effectively%20insider%20trading%20rings%20where%20he%20would%20get%20a%20bunch%20of%20wealthy%20guys%20together%20and%20say%2C%20'We're%20going%20to%20paint%20the%20tape%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20put%20some%20stories%20out%20saying%20the%20stock%20is%20going%20to%20go%20up%2C'%26quot%3B%20Sorkin%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20you%20would%20literally%20have%20the%20equivalent%20of%20almost%20like%20actors%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20exchange%20saying%2C%20'I'm%20buying%20for%20120%2C%20I'm%20buying%20for%20140%2C'%20and%20they%20all%20knew%20exactly%20how%20high%20it%20was%20going%20to%20go%2C%20and%20then%20they%20knew%20when%20they%20were%20going%20to%20pull%20the%20rug.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20were%20brokerages%20throughout%20the%20city%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Irene%20Bordini%20with%20WD%20Hutton%20at%20one%20of%20Hutton%20%26amp%3B%20Co.'s%20brokerage%20offices.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6904f9ef0be9845f2dc58138%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223795%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EActress%20Irene%20Bordini%20with%20WD%20Hutton%20at%20one%20of%20Hutton%20%26amp%3B%20Co.'s%20brokerage%20offices.%3Cp%3EUnderwood%20Archives%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20there%20weren't%20Robinhood%20or%20Schwab%20mobile%20apps%20back%20then.%20Many%20people%20would%20buy%20stocks%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20meant%20that%20there%20were%20physical%20brokerage%20locations%20sprinkled%20throughout%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProhibition%20was%20happening%2C%20so%20all%20the%20bars%20were%20closed%2C%20and%20the%20national%20pastime%20had%20become%20speculating%2C%20and%20there%20were%20literally%20brokerages%20on%20the%20corners%20of%20streets%20like%20they're%20a%20Starbucks%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Sorkin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EYou%20could%20trade%20on%20margin%20easily%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20wi