0prominent%20individuals%20to%20the%20algorithm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbellecommunication.com%2Fhow-social-media-influencers-are-reshaping-restaurant-discovery-and-choice-for-gen-z-millennials%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarch%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20conducted%20in%20partnership%20with%20Belle%20Communication%20and%20Nation's%20Restaurant%20News%2C%2073%25%20of%20Gen%20Z%20and%20millennial%20respondents%20said%20a%20social%20media%20review%20led%20them%20to%20visit%20a%20restaurant%20in%20the%20past%20three%20months%2C%20while%20%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22rgba(0%2C%200%2C%200%2C%200)%5C%22%3E43.7%25%20said%20they%20go%20to%20social%20media%20first%20for%20restaurant%20recommendations%3C%2Fmark%3E.%20Meanwhile%2C%2038.6%25%20said%20they%20use%20social%20review%20sites%20like%20Google%20or%20Yelp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20comes%20down%20to%20where%20they're%20spending%20the%20majority%20of%20their%20time%2C%20which%20is%20online%2C%26quot%3B%20Hughes%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20on%20platforms%20like%20Instagram%20and%20TikTok.%20That's%20where%20they%20go%20for%20inspiration%20for%20information%20across%20multiple%20facets%20of%20their%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHughes%20said%20there's%20a%20missed%20opportunity%20for%20restaurants%20that%20don't%20place%20value%20on%20social%20media%2C%20specifically%20influencer%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20people%20are%20being%20very%20selective%20with%20how%20they're%20spending%20their%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BConsumers%20are%20dining%20out%20less%2C%20and%20everyone%20is%20trying%20to%20capture%20the%20attention%20of%20Gen%20Z.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElizabeth%20Clayton%2C%20a%2026-year-old%20living%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20said%20she%20regularly%20sends%20and%20receives%20restaurant%20reviews%20from%20Instagram%20or%20TikTok%20to%20friends%20and%20group%20chats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20review%20from%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-change-food-influencer-family-support-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efood%20influencer%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20catch%20her%20eye%20if%20there's%20something%20unique%20about%20the%20restaurant's%20interior%20or%20the%20presentation%20of%20its%20food.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20short-form%20content%2C%20that's%20what%20will%20get%20me%20to%20stop%20scrolling%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFood%20influencers%20and%20collectives%20are%20leveraging%20this%20power.%20Five%20years%20after%20launching%20their%20handle%2C%20Audrey%20Jongens%20and%20Meg%20Radice%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftheviplist%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20VIP%20List%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20carved%20out%20a%20place%20on%20social%20media%20for%20their%20unfiltered%2C%20%26quot%3Bbrutally%20honest%26quot%3B%20restaurant%20reviews%20of%20famous%20haunts%20like%20Rao's%2C%20Carbone%2C%20and%20Red%20Hook%20Tavern%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222056%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Audrey%20Jongens%20and%20Meg%20Radice%20attend%20the%20Universal%20Pictures%20and%20Blumhous'%20special%20screening%20for%20SPEAK%20NO%20EVIL%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d418cbf9db348adc0c1433%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221542%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFood%20influencers%20Audrey%20Jongens%20and%20Meg%20Radice%20of%20The%20VIP%20List%20are%20changing%20how%20younger%20generations%20consume%20food%20reviews.%3Cp%3EEugene%20Gologursky%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Universal%20Pictures%20and%20Blumhouse%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fast-paced%20reviews%2C%20created%20for%20TikTok%20or%20Instagram%20Reels%2C%20are%20made%20by%20cutting%20together%20multiple%20clips%20filmed%20during%20a%20meal%20and%20narrated%20with%20evocative%20words%20like%20%26quot%3Bcreamy%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdecadent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20used%20to%20have%20to%20read%20a%20super%20long%20paragraph%20or%20essay%20about%20a%20restaurant%20to%20know%20if%20it%20was%20any%20good%2C%20and%20I%20just%20don't%20think%20that%20anyone%20even%20has%20the%20time%20to%20do%20that%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jongens%2C%20a%20Gen%20Z-Millennial%20cusper%20who%20also%20uses%20TikTok%20when%20searching%20where%20to%20eat.%20%26quot%3BNever%20once%20am%20I%20going%20to%20Yelp%20or%20Google.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20over%20140%2C000%20followers%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftheviplist%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20450%2C000%20followers%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40theviplist%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20duo%20is%20gaining%20traction%20with%20city%20diners%20and%20out-of-towners.%20Even%20though%20it's%20trending%20with%20Gen%20Z%2C%20The%20VIP%20List's%20following%20still%20falls%20short%20of%20traditional%20review%20platforms%2C%20such%20as%20The%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20which%20has%20a%20cooking%20account%20where%20columnists%20share%20similar%20short-form%20video%20reviews%20of%20restaurants%20to%20its%204.5%20million%20Instagram%20followers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times'%20audience%20tends%20to%20skew%20older%20%E2%80%94%20according%20to%20a%20recent%20study%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fshort-reads%2F2025%2F08%2F28%2Fhow-the-audiences-of-30-major-news-sources-differ-by-age%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPew%20Research%20Center%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20average%20age%20of%20a%20New%20York%20Times%20reader%20is%2043.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDLnULmQRffU%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDLnULmQRffU%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDLnULmQRffU%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20VIP%20List%20(%40theviplist)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EHughes%20said%20follower%20counts%20aren't%20always%20the%20best%20indicator%20of%20what%20will%20drive%20foot%20traffic%20to%20a%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20best%20results%20and%20the%20most%20impact%20when%20working%20with%20influencers%20come%20from%20those%20micro-creators%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20which%20she%20defined%20as%20creators%20with%20between%2010%2C000%20and%20100%2C000%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20visual%20appeal%20of%20food%20reviews%2C%20Hughes%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Brelatability%26quot%3B%20of%20food%20influencers%20is%20what%20attracts%20viewers.%20Some%20influencers%20are%20also%20known%20for%20sharing%20honest%20reviews%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20that%20honesty%20can%20create%20that%20trust%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20That's%20true%20of%20Jongens%20and%20Radice%2C%20neither%20of%20whom%20has%20a%20professional%20culinary%20background%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fact%20they%20say%20makes%20them%20more%20relatable%20to%20their%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFood%20criticism%20is%20probably%20one%20of%20the%20most%20pretentious%20industries%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Radice%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20talking%20Michelin%2C%20'I'm%20a%20sommelier%2C'%20all%20this%20stuff.%20'The%20wine%20smells%20of%20sandalwood.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20need%20to%20know%20all%20these%20terms%20to%20know%20if%20the%20food%20tastes%20good%20or%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20don't%20hold%20back%2C%20Jongens%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20come%20with%20receipts.%20We're%20not%20only%20telling%20you%20about%20the%20food%2C%20we%20are%20%3Cem%3Eshowing%3C%2Fem%3E%20everything.%20When%20a%20restaurant%20sucks%2C%20we%20can%20literally%20show%20why%20%E2%80%94%20and%20when%20a%20restaurant%20is%20amazing%2C%20we%20can%20also%20show%20that%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20mistrust%20in%20influencers%20%E2%80%94%20who%20might%20be%20paid%20by%20a%20business%20or%20receive%20a%20free%20meal%20in%20exchange%20for%20posting%20about%20it%20%E2%80%94%20can%20run%20high.%20Clayton%20said%20she%20trusts%20Google%20and%20Yelp%20reviews%20because%20she%20feels%20that%20those%20users%20have%20less%20to%20gain%20from%20posting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInfluencers%2C%20however%2C%20have%20standards%20that%20they%20abide%20by%20to%20maintain%20their%20credibility.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERadice%20said%20that%20while%20she%20and%20Jongens%20occasionally%20accept%20complimentary%20meals%2C%20they%20never%20post%20reviews%20in%20exchange%20for%20them.%20At%20most%2C%20they%20might%20share%20a%20photo%20from%20the%20visit%2C%20but%20they%20won't%20publicly%20comment%20on%20the%20food%20unless%20they've%20paid%20for%20it%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20even%20when%20money%20or%20access%20changes%20hands%2C%20Hughes%20said%2C%20smaller%20or%20local%20creators%20can%20act%20as%20valuable%20extensions%20of%20a%20restaurant's%20team%20who%20don't%20have%20the%20time%20or%20resources%20to%20produce%20engaging%20social%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20something%20Pietro%20Quaglia%20knows%20well.%20His%20bubble-gum%20pink%20Italian%20restaurant%2C%20Pietro%20Nolita%2C%20reaped%20the%20benefits%20of%20its%20Insta-fame%20during%20the%202010s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Guests%20attend%20a%20Trans%20Awareness%20Dinner%20held%20at%20Pietro%20Nolita%20on%20March%2013%2C%202018%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68dd49e6cc993f9955cf4c2a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGuests%20attend%20a%20Trans%20Awareness%20Dinner%20held%20at%20Pietro%20Nolita%20on%20March%2013%2C%202018.%3Cp%3EDia%20Dipasupil%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20years%2C%20we%20had%20a%20strong%20presence%20on%20Instagram%20and%20TikTok%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20it%20was%20sometimes%20for%20the%20wrong%20reasons%2C%26quot%3B%20Quaglia%20said%20over%20email.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20our%20playful%20slogan%2C%20'Pink%20as%20F***%2C'%20and%20people%20came%20in%20droves%20to%20post%20photos%2C%20but%20often%20just%20because%20it%20was%20pink%20and%20kitschy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BNot%20many%20cared%20or%20understood%20about%20the%20homemade%20fresh%20pasta%20that%20took%20hours%20to%20prepare%2C%20or%20the%20sauces%20that%20took%20even%20longer%2C%20and%20all%20the%20ingredients%20we%20imported%20from%20Italy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Manhattan%20restaurant%20underwent%20a%20revamp%20in%20February%2C%20swapping%20the%20pink%20for%20burgundy%2C%20focusing%20more%20on%20its%20food%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bstepping%20a%20bit%20away%20from%20the%20hyper-social-media%20aesthetic%2C%26quot%3B%20Quaglia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20he%20said%2C%20he%20believes%20social%20media%20is%20important%20for%20reaching%20younger%20audiences.%20And%20those%20audiences%20are%20getting%20broader.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsproutsocial.com%2Finsights%2Fnew-social-media-demographics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESprout%20Social%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20in%20February%20that%2060%25%20of%20Instagram%20users%20were%20under%20the%20age%20of%2035.%20Yet%2078%25%20of%20Gen%20Xers%20have%20an%20Instagram%20profile%2C%20according%20to%20the%20agency's%202024%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJongens%20and%20Radice%20both%20said%20their%20typical%20audience%20encompasses%20Gen%20Z%2C%20but%20millennials%20are%20also%20a%20core%20part%20of%20their%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMillennials%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20can%20afford%20the%20places%20we%20go%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Radice%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20posting%20three%20Michelin-star%20meals.%20In%20college%2C%20I%20couldn't%20afford%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhatever%20their%20age%2C%20diners%20are%20still%20hungry%20for%20opinions.%20For%20some%2C%20social%20media%20feeds%20are%20the%20new%20Zagat%20guide%2C%20and%20traditional%20print%20reviews%20are%20starting%20to%20taste%20a%20little%20stale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20one%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20swapped%20for%20the%20other.%20Hughes%20believes%20that%20traditional%20restaurant%20reviews%20and%20influencer%20content%20can%20coexist%20and%20may%20even%20better%20leverage%20restaurants%20for%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20when%20combined%2C%20that's%20where%20the%20greatest%20power%20lies%20for%20restaurants%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-restaurant-discovery-social-medi