%20Diljit%20shares%20hilarious%20moment%20with%20cricketers%20-%20Watch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1761987679000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-125013163%2Cimgsize-46514.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Findia-vs-australia%2Fgod-bless-you-all-diljit-dosanjh-shares-hilarious-moment-with-indian-cricketers-in-australia-watch%2Farticleshow%2F125012460.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Diljit%20Dosanjh%2C%20facing%20recent%20criticism%2C%20shared%20a%20heartwarming%20Instagram%20post%20with%20cricketers%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20and%20Jitesh%20Sharma%20in%20Australia.%20The%20trio%20recreated%20a%20viral%20moment%20from%20their%20%26quot%3BGod%20Bless%26quot%3B%20song%2C%20with%20Jitesh%20humorously%20repeating%20his%20modified%20lyric.%20This%20friendly%20reunion%2C%20blending%20music%20and%20cricket%2C%20has%20garnered%20significant%20positive%20fan%20attention%2C%20showcasing%20Dosanjh's%20enduring%20appeal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Findia-vs-australia%2Fgod-bless-you-all-diljit-dosanjh-shares-hilarious-moment-with-indian-cricketers-in-australia-watch%2Farticleshow%2F125012460.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20tried%20Grokipedia%20and%20I%20think%20it%20beats%20Wikipedia%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20in%20some%20cases.%20(Citation%20needed.)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22grokipedia%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690505d10be9845f2dc5832e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGrokipedia%2C%20Elon%20Musk's%20alternative%20to%20Wikipedia.%3Cp%3ENikolas%20Kokovlis%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrokipedia-vs-wikipedia-differences-compared-elon-musk-2025-10%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGrokipedia%20is%20Elon%20Musk's%20alternative%20to%20Wikipedia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20focusing%20on%20less%20%26quot%3Bwoke%26quot%3B%20content.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20lot%20of%20the%20non-political%20entries%20are%20just%20direct%20copies%20of%20Wikipedia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20in%20certain%20cases%2C%20Grokipedia%20improved%20the%20Wikipedia%20page%20%E2%80%94%20padding%20out%20information%20and%20sources.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20admit%20I'm%20fairly%20skeptical%20of%20the%20results%20of%20xAI's%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwikipedia-elon-musk-comment-grokipedia-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGrokipedia%20and%20its%20mission%20to%20be%20an%20anti-woke%20version%20of%20Wikipedia%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20after%20testing%20it%20out%20a%20little%20bit%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20find%20that%2C%20in%20certain%20cases%2C%20it%20seems%20better%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwikipedia-traffic-down-ai-answers-elon-musk-grokipedia-wikimedia-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWikipedia%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20its%20entries%20for%20hot-button%20things%20like%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bgender%26quot%3B%20are%20exactly%20what%20you'd%20expect%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Bunbiased%26quot%3B%20mission.%20It%20hurts%20my%20head%20to%20think%20about%20this%20too%20much%2C%20so%20I%20won't%20linger%20on%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20most%20pages%20are%20not%20hotbeds%20of%20%26quot%3Bwokism%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20they%20end%20up%20almost%20word-for-word%20identical%20to%20Wikipedia.%20(Grokipedia%20is%20able%20to%20essentially%20copy%20from%20Wikipedia%20because%20Wikipedia%20allows%20itself%20to%20be%20scraped%20by%20AI%20bots).%20So%20far%2C%20Grokipedia%20has%20about%20800%2C000%20pages%2C%20whereas%20Wikipedia's%20English-language%20version%20has%20over%207%20million.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ExAI%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20how%20Grokipedia%20pages%20were%20chosen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20things%20I%20compared%20was%20the%20entries%20for%20the%202008%20animated%20movie%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgrokipedia.com%2Fpage%2FBolt_(2008_film)%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBolt%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20a%20superhero%20dog%20is%20voiced%20by%20John%20Travolta.%20(I%20had%20happened%20to%20look%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FBolt_(2008_film)%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWikipedia%3C%2Fa%3E%20page%20for%20it%20while%20my%20kid%20was%20watching%20the%20movie%20recently.)%20As%20you%20can%20probably%20imagine%2C%20this%20isn't%20a%20particularly%20political%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20movie%20entries%2C%20Grokipedia's%20has%20a%20plot%20summary%2C%20some%20production%20details%2C%20a%20cast%20list%2C%20and%20an%20overview%20of%20the%20critical%20reception.%20(I%20asked%20ChatGPT%20to%20compare%20the%20two%20articles%20to%20see%20which%20had%20more%20%26quot%3Bbias%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20in%20a%20case%20of%20AI-on-AI%20crime%2C%20ChatGPT%20accused%20Grok%20of%20having%20a%20pro-corporate%20bias%20by%20taking%20only%20Disney%20execs'%20word%20on%20some%20of%20the%20elements%20of%20production.%20Ha!)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a72cb56a-69b9-452c-94e1-cd94b194de6b%5C%22%3EWhere%20Elon%20Musk%20might%20be%20onto%20something%20with%20Grokipedia%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20browsing%20around%20Grokipedia%20for%20a%20while%2C%20I%20came%20across%20some%20things%20that%20seemed%20particularly%20promising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20types%20of%20pages%20where%20Grokipedia%20seemed%20to%20beat%20Wikipedia%20were%20the%20unloved%2C%20scraggly%20entries%20on%20Wikipedia.%20You%20know%20the%20kind%20%E2%80%94%20where%20it%20truly%20seems%20like%20a%20bunch%20of%20people%20added%20in%20a%20single%20sentence%20once%20a%20year%20for%20the%20last%2015%20years.%20Where%20the%20writing%20lacks%20cohesion%2C%20tiny%20details%20are%20given%20equal%20prominence%20alongside%20big%20facts%2C%20and%20the%20result%20is%20generally%20a%20mess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20an%20example%20of%20one%20of%20these.%20I%20had%20recently%20looked%20up%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FDana_Hall_School%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWikipedia%20entry%20for%20the%20Dana%20Hall%20School%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20fancy%20girls'%20private%20school%20near%20Boston%20where%20the%20recent%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%20winner%20attended.%20The%20entry%20isn't%20short%2C%20but%20it's%20disorganized%2C%20with%20a%20lengthy%20%26quot%3Bhistory%26quot%3B%20section%20that%20reads%20like%20a%20list%20of%20disjointed%20bullet%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Grokipedia%20version%20felt%20much%20more%20thorough%20and%20organized%20into%20sections%20about%20its%20history%2C%20academics%2C%20facilities%2C%20admissions%2C%20and%20impact.%20This%20is%20one%20of%20those%20things%20where%20there%20is%20lots%20of%20solid%20information%20about%20it%20existing%20out%20there%20on%20the%20internet%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20has%20been%20added%20so%20far%20to%20the%20Wikipedia%20page%20by%20real%20humans%20%E2%80%94%20and%20an%20AI%20can%20crawl%20the%20web%20to%20find%20these%20sources%20and%20turn%20it%20into%20text.%20(Note%3A%20I%20did%20not%20fact-check%20Grokipedia's%20entry%2C%20and%20it's%20totally%20possible%20it%20got%20all%20sorts%20of%20stuff%20wrong!)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20will%20note%20that%20there%20are%20some%20unusual%20aspects%20to%20the%20entry%2C%20however.%20There's%20a%20whole%20section%20that%20talks%20about%20the%20arguments%20for%20and%20against%20single-sex%20education%20and%20a%20discussion%20of%20the%20school's%20racial%20diversity%20that%20has%20more%20than%20a%20whiff%20of%20an%20anti-DEI%20agenda.%20My%20head%20hurts%20again%2C%20so%20let's%20set%20that%20aside%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22711ab245-4f10-4d47-a469-7fba2695fe57%5C%22%3EAI%20might%20be%20of%20some%20help%20to%20Wikipedia%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20can%20see%20is%20a%20version%20where%20AI%20is%20able%20to%20flesh%20out%20certain%20types%20of%20articles%20and%20improve%20them%20with%20additional%20information%20from%20reliable%20sources.%20In%20my%20poking%20around%2C%20I%20found%20a%20few%20other%20cases%20like%20this%3A%20entries%20for%20small%20towns%2C%20which%20are%20often%20sparse%20on%20Wikipedia%2C%20are%20filled%20out%20more%20robustly%20on%20Grokipedia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20interesting%20example%3A%20By%20clicking%20%26quot%3BRandom%20article%26quot%3B%20on%20Wikipedia%20and%20searching%20for%20corresponding%20Grokipedia%20entries%2C%20I%20found%20a%20curious%20case%20where%20the%20two%20entries%20differ%20slightly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20case%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgrokipedia.com%2Fpage%2FBaroness_Mary_Vetsera%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBaroness%20Marie%20Vetsera%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20woman%20involved%20in%20a%20minor%2018th-century%20royal%20scandal%2C%20Wikipedia%20had%20a%20substantial%20entry.%20But%20Grokipedia's%20was%20even%20longer%2C%20and%20formatted%20quite%20differently%20%E2%80%94%20and%20frankly%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20told%20a%20better%20narrative%20of%20the%20baroness's%20untimely%20demise.%20But%20it%20also%20had%20some%20bad%20quirks.%20For%20example%2C%20Grokipedia%20used%20a%20citation%20for%20a%20Facebook%20page%20about%20royal%20history%20that%20seemed%20to%20be%20viral%20clickbait%20written%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20Grokipedia%20is%20not%20perfect%20%E2%80%94%20far%2C%20far%20from%20it.%20But%20it's%20an%20in