d%3D%5C%2233838ab4-e8f0-4cda-a4b4-2e4074fda026%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20money%20is%20tight%2C%20work%20takes%20precedence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223248%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22David%20Hugo%20Barret%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6900e90f0be9845f2dc53cd4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222436%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDavid%20Hugo%20Barrett%20works%20as%20a%20substitute%20teacher.%3Cp%3ETimothy%20Wolfer%2F%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Hugo%20Barrett%2C%2082%2C%20begins%20every%20middle%20and%20high%20school%20class%20he%20teaches%20with%20life%20lessons%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20working%20hard%20and%20staying%20out%20of%20trouble.%20For%20a%20few%20hours%20each%20day%2C%20he%20feels%20young%2C%20learning%20Gen%20Alpha%20slang%20and%20staying%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20latest%20tech%20trends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20he%20returns%20home%20each%20night%2C%20he's%20reminded%20of%20the%20disabilities%20that%20have%20made%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-market-hiring-unemployment-labor-force-participation-immigration-tariffs-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoutlook%3C%2Fa%3E%20less%20stable.%20He%20has%20lymphedema%2C%20which%20leads%20to%20swelling%20in%20his%20legs%2C%20and%20peripheral%20neuropathy%2C%20which%20causes%20nerve%20damage%20in%20his%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20say%20age%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20number.%20That's%20just%20simply%20not%20true%2C%26quot%3B%20Barrett%20said.%20%26quot%3BAging%20is%20not%20something%20that%20can%20be%20taken%20lightly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarrett%20works%20as%20a%20substitute%20teacher%20in%20Maryland%2C%20having%20spent%20decades%20as%20a%20systems%20engineer%20and%20teacher.%20He%20retired%20in%202018%20and%20self-published%20his%20memoir%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20Newark%20Childhood%2C%26quot%3B%20before%20returning%20to%20work%20part-time%2