inking-machine-labs-valuation-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20firm%20started%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20former%20OpenAI%20CTO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmira-murati-openai-startup-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMira%20Murati%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20raised%20%242%20billion%20in%20a%20seed%20round%20earlier%20this%20year%20at%20a%20%2412%20billion%20valuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVenture%20capitalists%20are%20pouring%20billions%20into%20startups%20led%20by%20prominent%20researchers%2C%20betting%20that%20the%20next%20breakthrough%20in%20AI%20will%20come%20from%20small%2C%20talent-rich%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20round%20is%20still%20in%20progress%2C%20and%20terms%20could%20change.%20Zelikman%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZelikman%2C%20a%20Ph.D.%20student%20in%20computer%20science%20at%20Stanford%2C%20is%20best%20known%20for%20being%20the%20lead%20author%20of%20a%20paper%20last%20year%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenreview.net%2Fforum%3Fid%3DoRXPiSOGH9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edetailing%20how%20language%20models%20can%20teach%20themselves%20to%20think%20before%20speaking.%20%3C%2Fa%3EBefore%20joining%20the%20technical%20staff%20at%20xAI%20in%202024%2C%20Zelikman%20was%20a%20machine%20learning%20intern%20at%20Microsoft%20and%20also%20a%20deep%20learning%20engineer%20at%20Lazard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZelikman%20believes%20today's%20language%20models%20are%20too%20cold%20and%20machine-like%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOh0oQnKn9dw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20told%20venture%20capitalist%20Sarah%20Guo%20on%20her%20podcast%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20fundamental%20thing%20is%20that%20the%20models%20kind%20of%20don't%20understand%20the%20long-term%20implications%20of%20the%20things%20that%20they%20do%20and%20say%2C%20when%20you%20treat%20every%20turn%20of%20a%20conversation%20as%20its%20