the%20fabrics%20were%20after%20regular%20wear.%20Every%20coat%20was%20judged%20on%20how%20well%20it%20balanced%20style%20and%20function.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f3a42e9b-268d-4fc8-81aa-ef46776c5b52%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20trench%20coat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFit%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20ideal%20fit%20depends%20on%20the%20look%20and%20function%20you%20want.%20A%20classic%20trench%20coat%20typically%20has%20a%20closer%20fit%20with%20a%20defined%20waist%2C%20often%20enhanced%20by%20a%20belt%20or%20subtle%20tailoring.%20This%20creates%20a%20polished%2C%20hourglass%20silhouette%20that%20works%20over%20light%20layers.%20More%20modern%20or%20oversized%20silhouettes%20may%20offer%20a%20roomier%20fit%20that%20prioritizes%20comfort%20and%20layering%20heavier%20sweaters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%20quality%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMost%20modern%20trenches%20are%20made%20from%20cotton%2C%20polyester%2C%20or%20a%20blend%2C%20often%20with%20added%20stretch%20or%20a%20water-repellent%20finish.%20Premium%20options%20may%20include%20sustainably%20sourced%20or%20OEKO-TEX%20certified%20fabrics.%20Choose%20a%20material%20that%20feels%20sturdy%20but%20not%20stiff%20and%20has%20a%20smooth%20drape%20that%20flatters%20your%20frame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeather%20resistance%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20you%20plan%20to%20wear%20your%20trench%20regularly%2C%20water-repellent%20or%20waterproof%20fabrics%20are%20a%20must.%20Some%20are%20also%20wind-resistant%2C%20which%20adds%20extra%20comfort%20on%20chilly%2C%20breezy%20days.%20Fully%20seam-sealed%20styles%20offer%20the%20most%20protection%2C%20while%20lightweight%20water-resistant%20versions%20work%20well%20for%20transitional%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%20and%20warmth%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20lightweight%20trench%20is%20perfect%20for%20spring%20and%20early%20fall%2C%20while%20lined%20or%20insulated%20options%20add%20warmth%20for%20even%20cooler%20temper