20is%20experiencing%20rapid%20growth%2C%20driven%20by%20technological%20advancements%20and%20infrastructure%20investments.%20But%20scaling%20up%20depends%20on%20making%20the%20vehicles%20safe%20and%20ready%20for%20drivers%20and%20riders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20virtual%20event%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCbtbN4dyfwE%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInside%20Self-Driving%3A%20The%20AI-Driven%20Evolution%20of%20Autonomous%20Vehicles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20presented%20by%20Mobileye%2C%20a%20panel%20of%20experts%20from%20across%20the%20autonomous%20industry%2C%20discussed%20how%20the%20technology%20is%20transforming%20and%20how%20automakers%2C%20tech%20innovators%2C%20and%20policymakers%20are%20collaborating%20to%20make%20the%20vehicles%20safe%20and%20scalable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20two%20sessions%2C%20they%20examined%20the%20state%20of%20AV%20technology%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20as%20well%20as%20customer%20perception%20and%20adoption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c4378b55-c2b8-4cf6-b579-cbad2a77ba4f%5C%22%3ECollaborating%20to%20Scale%20Autonomous%20Vehicles%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EScaling%20AV%20technology%20depends%20on%20proving%20to%20users%20and%20regulators%20that%20the%20vehicles%20are%20safe%2C%20said%20AI%20expert%20Dr.%20Deborah%20Berebichez%2C%20kicking%20off%20the%20first%20session%20covering%20Mobileye's%20collaboration%20with%20Lyft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20consumers%2C%20AVs%20have%20been%20something%20of%20a%20novelty%2C%20said%20Stephen%20Hayes%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20autonomous%2C%20fleets%2C%20and%20driver%20operations%20at%20Lyft.%20To%20change%20that%2C%20he%20said%2C%20companies%20like%20his%20need%20to%20educate%20users%20about%20the%20technology%2C%20emphasize%20its%20safety%2C%20and%20ensure%20that%20riders'%20experiences%20with%20AVs%20are%20%26quot%3Bdelightful%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20that%20they%20opt%20in%20for%20future%20autonomous%20trips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemonstrating%20that%20AV%20crash%20rates%20are%20lower%20than%20human%20drivers'%20is%20a%20key%20data%20point%20for%20regulators%2C%20said%20JJ%20Jungwirth%2C%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20autonomous%20vehicles%20at%20Mobileye.%20It's%20also%20important%20to%20show%20that%20the%20technology%20%26quot%3Bnever%20sleeps%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20surrounded%20by%20sensors%20and%20cameras%20that%20%26quot%3Breact%20in%20milliseconds%2C%26quot%3B%20much%20faster%20than%20humans%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20regulators%20should%20understand%20that%20special%20lanes%20or%20other%20infrastructure%20aren't%20necessary%20for%20roadways%20to%20accommodate%20AVs%2C%20Jungwirth%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPartnerships%20are%20also%20crucial%2C%20Hayes%20emphasized.%20%26quot%3BThe%20market%20opportunity%20here%20is%20enormous.%20More%20players%20are%20realizing%20that%20we%20can%20go%20further%20by%20finding%20partners%20that%20have%20very%20complementary%20skill%20sets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22883e5b49-3c16-4653-924c-a97beaea26f3%5C%22%3EMaking%20Autonomy%20Work%20for%20Everyone%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAVs%20are%20ready%20to%20accommodate%20drivers%20and%20passengers%2C%20and%20are%20in%20the%20phase%20where%20%26quot%3Bfull%20autonomy%20has%20gone%20from%20the%20science%20project%20into%20an%20actual%20product%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20James%20Philbin%2C%20head%20of%20autonomy%20at%20Rivian%2C%20during%20the%20second%20session%2C%20which%20focused%20on%20how%20cities%2C%20automakers%2C%20and%20regulators%20are%20making%20the%20technology%20work%20for%20everyday%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20significant%20AV%20deployments%20in%20certain%20cities%2C%20such%20as%20San%20Francisco%2C%20and%20Philbin%20said%20he%20expects%20that%20to%20scale%20up%20quickly.%20He%20believes%20the%20next%20phase%20will%20involve%20incorporating%20more%20personally%20owned%20self-driving%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20challenge%20is%20integrating%20AVs%20into%20existing%20transportation%20networks%20as%20the%20technology%20expands%2C%20said%20Charlie%20Tyson%2C%20technology%20activation%20director%20of%20Michigan's%20Office%20of%20Future%20Mobility%20and%20Electrification.%20This%20is%20something%20Michigan%20is%20currently%20working%20on%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20is%20to%20get%20drivers%20more%20comfortable%20with%20AVs%20and%20normalize%20using%20them%2C%20Philbin%20says.%20He%20expects%20AV%20taxis%20to%20become%20ubiquitous%20in%20the%20coming%20years%20and%20personal%20vehicles%20to%20have%20more%20autonomous%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETyson%20adds%20that%20the%20public%20needs%20more%20opportunities%20to%20%26quot%3Bexperience%20the%20technology.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20pilot%20projects%20in%20Michigan%20revealed%20that%20nearly%20all%20AV%20riders%20would%20take%20another%20trip%20in%20an%20AV%20and%20recommend%20it%20to%20their%20peers.%20However%2C%20they%20felt%20less%20comfortable%20without%20a%20human%20safety%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20the%20trust%20issue%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20persistent%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20Philbin%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20people%20get%20more%20used%20to%20those%20high%20levels%20of%20autonomy%2C%20they'll%20expect%20more%20autonomy%20in%20their%20vehicles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAV%20makers%20are%20working%20to%20advance%20the%20technology%2C%20such%20as%20ensuring%20the%20vehicles%20adapt%20to%20harsh%20weather%20conditions%20and%20high-population%20densities%2C%20and%20collecting%20data%20on%20how%20people%20drive%20in%20these%20situations%2C%20Philbin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20Tyson%20said%20the%20industry%20is%20focused%20on%20debunking%20the%20biggest%20myth%20about%20AVs%3A%20that%20the%20technology%20isn't%20ready%20for%20everyday%20consumers%20or%20that%20it's%20unsafe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20just%20the%20opposite%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BLet's%20get%20these%20vehicles%20out%20there%2C