0don't%20feel%20comfortable%20right%20away.%20In%20Albania%2C%20within%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20of%20wandering%20around%2C%20we%20felt%20like%20we%20belonged%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESandra%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20felt%20like%20a%20gut%20instinct%20that%20this%20place%20was%20good%20for%20us.%20The%20culture%20here%20is%20all%20about%20taking%20care%20of%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJeff%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20were%20talking%20to%20a%20tourism%20official%20here%20in%20Pogradec%20the%20other%20day%2C%20and%20he%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-woman-closed-business-moved-to-albania-cheap-rent-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAlbania%20is%20known%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20house%20of%20God%20and%20the%20house%20of%20guests.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESandra%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20They%20really%20do%20take%20care%20of%20their%20guests.%20For%20instance%2C%20when%20we%20first%20moved%20into%20our%20current%20apartment%2C%20the%20day%20after%20we%20arrived%2C%20there%20were%20a%20couple%20of%20things%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20fixed.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20handyman%20came%2C%20but%20also%20the%20landlord's%20aunt%20or%20cousin%2C%20and%20they%20brought%20over%20lunch%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2202e45621-b8d5-424f-96d4-817219939b9c%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20pros%20and%20cons%20to%20living%20here%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESandra%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERight%20now%2C%20we're%20living%20in%20a%20three-bedroom%2C%20two-bath%20apartment%20in%20Pogradec.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20a%20full%20kitchen%2C%20a%20washer%2C%20and%20three%20balconies%20overlooking%20Lake%20Ohrid.%20We're%20on%20a%20short-term%20rental%2C%20and%20our%20monthly%20payment%2C%20including%20utilities%20and%20high-speed%20internet%2C%20averages%20about%20%241%2C100%20a%20month%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20huge%20apartment%20for%20the%20price.%20If%20we%20were%20to%20do%20a%20year%20lease%2C%2