vind%20Srinivas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ee84cd1c1f80efbec5906a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221791%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPerplexity%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Aravind%20Srinivas.%3Cp%3EAraya%20Doheny%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Gold%20House%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20search%20engine%20startup%20Perplexity%20has%20been%20raising%20back-to-back%20funding%20rounds.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20startup%20got%20fundraise%20offers%20at%20valuations%20from%20%2414%20billion%20to%20%2450%20billion%20in%20just%20a%20few%20months.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20investors%20worry%20that%20the%20startup%20is%20getting%20ahead%20of%20itself%20as%20the%20market%20fears%20an%20AI%20bubble.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20new%20AI%20gold%20rush%2C%20startups%20aren't%20raising%20money%20every%20year%3B%20they're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startups-rapid-funding-rounds-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraising%20massive%20rounds%20every%20month.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Perplexity%2C%20the%20buzzy%20AI%20search%20challenger%20to%20Google%2C%20has%20become%20the%20poster%20child%20for%20back-to-back%20fundraising%2C%20facing%20investor%20demand%20at%20valuations%20from%20%2414%20billion%20to%20as%20high%20as%20%2450%20billion%20in%20just%20a%20few%20months%2C%20Business%20Insider%20has%20learned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20frenzy%20is%20fueling%20investor%20FOMO%20%E2%80%94%20and%20fears%20of%20a%20modern-day%20bubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerplexity%20and%20its%20peers%20are%20buoyed%20by%20AI%20juggernauts%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-market-share-700-billion-sam-altman-chatgpt-sora-ai-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cu%3E%20%3C%2Fu%3Eand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ceo-warning-world-ai-replacing-jobs-necessary-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20continue%20to%20raise%20money%20at%20eye-popping%20valuations.%20OpenAI%20was%20most%20recently%20valued%20at%20%24500%20billion%20in%20a%20secondary%20deal%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg%2C%20a%20rising%20tide%20that's%20lifting%20other%20AI%20boats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reported%20in%20August%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperplexity-valuation-jumps-to-20-billion-in-latest-fundraise-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPerplexity%20was%20raising%20more%20money%20at%20a%20%2420%20billion%20valuation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20just%20a%20month%20after%20the%20startup%20had%20grabbed%20fresh%20funding%20at%20an%20%2418%20billion%20valuation%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg.%20Two%20months%20before%20that%2C%20Perplexity%20had%20raised%20at%20a%20%2414%20billion%20valuation%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20people%20close%20to%20the%20company%20said%20Perplexity%20has%20recently%20fielded%20offers%20from%20outside%20investors%20at%20valuations%20as%20high%20as%20%2450%20billion.%20Those%20people%20didn't%20say%20how%20serious%20the%20offers%20were%20or%20whether%20Perplexity%20engaged%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20demand%20to%20invest%20in%20that%20company%20is%20beyond%20anything%20that%20we've%20seen%20in%20our%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20Perplexity%20investor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerplexity's%20head%20of%20communication%2C%20Jesse%20Dwyer%2C%20said%20Perplexity%20doesn't%20comment%20on%20its%20fundraising%20efforts%20or%20valuation%2C%20but%20said%20the%20company%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bcrystal-clear%20view%20of%20its%20value.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20never%20considered%20any%20numbers%20other%20than%20the%20ones%20we%20know%20to%20be%20true%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20an%20email%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20constant%20comparison%20with%20other%20top%20AI%20companies%20and%20the%20endless%20stream%20of%20investor%20excitement%20may%20be%20both%20a%20blessing%20and%20a%20curse%20for%20surging%20startups%20like%20Perplexity.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20faces%20outsize%20demand%20from%20both%20primary%20and%20secondary%20markets%20%E2%80%94%20Perplexity%20ranked%20%237%20on%20Forge%20Global's%20list%20of%20companies%20attracting%20the%20most%20secondary%20investor%20interest%20on%20its%20platform%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%2C%20just%20behind%20Anthropic%20at%20%235%2C%20OpenAI%20at%20%232%2C%20and%20xAI%20at%20%231.%20Its%20fundraising%20pace%20is%20dizzying%2C%20and%20its%20valuation%20sizable%2C%20given%20Perplexity's%20age%20and%20revenue%20%E2%80%94%20Perplexity%20is%20three%20years%20old%20and%20was%20bringing%20in%20over%20%24150%20million%20in%20annual%20recurring%20revenue%20by%20mid-2025%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20benchmarking%20inevitably%20takes%20place%20in%20founders'%20minds%20and%20in%20investors'%20minds%2C%20and%20it's%20kind%20of%20hard%20to%20escape%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kevin%20Spain%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20Emergence%20Capital%2C%20of%20top%20AI%20startups%20in%20general.%20%26quot%3BIf%20other%20comparable%20companies%20are%20raising%20at%20a%20certain%20price%2C%20that%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20expectation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20more%20investors%20have%20been%20sounding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-bubble-culture-dotcom-housing-crypto-different-vibes-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealarm%20bells%20about%20a%20bubble%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20rising%20revenue%20multiples%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-techs-ai-love-fest-getting-messy-openai-oracle-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecircular%20AI%20deals%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Another%20Perplexity%20investor%20said%20that%20as%20Perplexity's%20valuation%20rises%2C%20its%20chances%20of%20being%20acquired%20or%20going%20public%20at%20that%20new%20price%20appear%20slimmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20creates%20a%20dilemma%20for%20investors%20in%20startups%20like%20Perplexity%20that%20raise%20back-to-back%20rounds%2C%20which%20open%20opportunities%20for%20early%20investors%20to%20sell%20some%20of%20their%20shares%20while%20simultaneously%20intensifying%20their%20FOMO%3A%20What%20if%20Perplexity's%20valuation%20actually%20makes%20sense%20in%20an%20age%20where%20AI%20could%20rewrite%20entire%20economic%20playbooks%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepeated%20markups%20can%20be%20especially%20conflicting%20for%20growth-stage%20investors%2C%20said%20Terrence%20Rohan%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20Otherwise%20Fund%2C%20which%20invested%20early%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-got-rich-on-figma-ipo-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFigma%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvanta-valuation-2-billion-in-new-funding-round-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVanta%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20create%20internal%20debate%20and%20dialogue%2C%20100%25%2C%20if%20a%20startup%20is%20getting%20marked%20up%20beyond%20the%20firm's%20internal%20conviction%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohan%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%2C%20hey%2C%20they're%20raising%20again.%20We%20need%20to%20commit%20another%20%2450%20million%20just%20to%20hold%20our%20ownership.%20We%20don't%20quite%20have%20conviction%20here%20yet%2C%20but%20these%20other%20guys%20do.%20And%20if%20we%20don't%2C%20we%20could%20look%20silly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ad636c63-fb43-4c17-8aa6-7ae2d91a9d41%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERaising%20for%20name%20recognition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20constant%20fundraising%20pads%20AI%20companies'%20balance%20sheets%2C%20it's%20also%20helping%20them%20build%20brand%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20recent%20fundraises%20have%20sent%20shockwaves%20across%20the%20tech%20ecosystem.%20Startups%20next%20in%20line%20are%20watching%20their%20valuations%20climb%20as%20OpenAI%20raises%20the%20ceiling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20zeitgeist%20right%20now%20is%20more%20about%20raising%20aggressively%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohan%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20seemingly%20creating%20reputation%20and%20brands%20in%20itself%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20raising%20just%20on%20the%20traction%20or%20the%20business%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumers%20make%20up%20the%20foundation%20of%20Perplexity's%20business.%20The%20company's%20consumer-facing%20search%20engine%20offers%20both%20free%20and%20%2420-a-month%20tiers%2C%20and%20it's%20begun%20branching%20into%20e-commerce%2C%20launching%20a%20shopping%20feature%20in%20November.%20Perplexity%20has%20multiple%20enterprise%20deals%2C%20too%2C%20selling%20its%20premium%20search%20engine%20to%20companies%20like%20Zoom%20(which%20also%20offers%20a%20Perplexity-powered%20AI%20companion%20to%20Zoom%20business%20customers)%20and%20Nvidia%20(an%20investor%20in%20Perplexity).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222149%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Perplexity%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Aravind%20Srinivas%20speaks%20at%20TechCrunch%20Disrupt%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ee9f465dbc4fd10daad772%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221612%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPerplexity%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Aravind%20Srinivas.%3Cp%3EKimberly%20White%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20TechCrunch%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPerplexity%20also%20drew%20attention%20this%20year%20for%20making%20multiple%20public%20offers%20to%20acquire%20or%20merge%20with%20assets%20bigger%20than%20Perplexity%20itself.%20In%20July%2C%20the%20startup%20announced%20a%20%2434.5%20billion%20bid%20to%20buy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-search-antitrust-monopoly-case-decision-winners-losers-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20Chrome%20browser%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20tech%20giant's%20antitrust%20brawl%20with%20the%20Justice%20Department.%20Earlier%2C%20in%20January%2C%20Perplexity%20submitted%20a%20bid%20to%20merge%20with%20ByteDance's%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWall%20Street%20analysts%20and%20investors%20largely%20viewed%20Perplexity's%20Chrome%20bid%20as%20a%20publicity%20stunt%2C%20with%20some%20criticizing%20the%20move%20and%20others%20lauding%20it%20as%20marketing%20genius.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDwyer%20rejected%20the%20idea%20that%20the%20Google%20Chrome%20bid%20was%20a%20stunt.%20%26quot%3BAs%20much%20as%20I'd%20love%20to%20take%20credit%20for%20a%20publicity%20stunt%2C%20the%20reality%20is%20this%20was%20a%20very%20serious%20offer%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BDue%20to%20the%20ongoing%20trial%2C%20our%20role%20in%20it%2C%20and%20the%20centrality%20of%20Chrome%20to%20the%20upcoming%20ruling%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20inappropriate%20NOT%20to%20transparently%20share%20the%20offer%20with%20the%20press.%20It%20wasn't%20publicity%2C%20it%20was%20integrity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20criticisms%20from%20Perplexity's%20investors%20on%20the%20bid%2C%20Dwyer%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B%5Bexisting%5D%20investors%20who%20consider%20our%20Chrome%20offer%20a%20publicity%20stunt%20are%20either%20miffed%20that%20they%20weren't%20asked%20to%20participate%20in%20funding%20it%2C%20or%20they%20simply%20don't%20understand%20the%20new%20importance%20of%20the%20browser%20layer%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI%20(which%20would%20also%20explain%20why%20we%20didn't%20ask%20them%20to%20help%20us%20fund%20it).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESrinivas%20has%20further%20eschewed%20VC%20formalities%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperplexity-ceo-ai-not-pitch-decks-fundraising-aravind-srinivas-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Editching%20pitch%20decks%3C%2Fa%3E%20altogether%2C%20he%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Berkeley%20Haas%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20write%20a%20memo%20and%20I%20tell%20them%20you%20can%20do%20a%20Q%26amp%3BA%20and%20ask%20whatever%20you%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20Srinivas%20said%20of%20potential%20investors.%20%26quot%3BAnything%20else%20that%20is%20not%20internal%20data%2C%20you%20can%20ask%20Perplexity.%20Like%2C%20it%20already%20knows%20everything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d576f429-4129-42b0-94b1-664bd9fe1d5b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20rewrites%20investing%20rules%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBallooning%20valuations%20with%20little%20accompanying%20revenue%20growth%20have%20become%20a%20particular%20concern%20for%20some%20bubble-wary%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20the%202021%20venture%20boom%2C%20startup%20valuation-to-revenue%20ratios%20fell%20from%20triple-digit%20peaks%20to%20single%20digits.%20But%20AI%20has%20turned%20those%20standards%20upside%20down.%20With%20over%20%24150%20million%20in%20annual%20recurring%20revenue%20and%20a%20%2420%20billion%20valuation%2C%20Perplexity's%20multiple%20easily%20exceeds%20100x.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperplexity-makes-200-ai-browser-free-to-battle-ai-slop-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPerplexity%20also%20made%20its%20AI%20browser%20Comet%20free%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20month%2C%20shortly%20after%20pausing%20new%20advertising%20deals%20to%20reevaluate%20how%20advertising%20affects%20its%20user%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerplexity%20said%20making%20Comet%20free%20would%20help%20users%20combat%20%26quot%3BAI%20slop%26quot%3B%20by%20offering%20a%20search%20tool%20that%20prioritizes%20higher-quality%20sources.%20It's%20also%20a%20clear%20move%20to%20help%20Perplexity%20capture%20more%20users%20in%20its%20quest%20to%20overtake%20Google%20Search.%20Still%2C%20any%20resulting%20cut%20to%20Perplexity's%20revenue%20could%20stretch%20its%20multiple%20even%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpain%20said%20high%20multiples%20tend%20to%20matter%20more%20to%20growth%20stage%20investors%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20closer%20you%20get%20to%20the%20point%20of%20exit%2C%20the%20more%20you%20care%20about%20the%20multiple%20you're%20paying.%26quot%3B%20But%20at%20early%20stages%2C%20what%20matters%20most%20is%20how%20the%20startup's%20revenue%20could%20grow%20and%20what%20valuation%20those%20investors%20believe%20the%20company%20could%20ultimately%20achieve%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerplexity's%20proposed%20exit%20timeline%20would%20give%20those%20investors%20more%20room%20to%20breathe.%20Srinivas%20said%20in%20a%20March%20Reddit%20post%20that%20Perplexity%20has%20%26quot%3Bno%20plans%20of%20IPOing%20before%202028.%26quot%3B%20And%20Perplexity%20is%20growing%20fast%20%E2%80%94%20its%20%24150%20million%20annualized%20revenue%20in%20mid-2025%20was%20more%20than%20quadruple%20its%20ARR%2C%20a%20projection%20of%20a%20company's%20annual%20revenue%2C%20a%20year%20prior%2C%20Business%20Insider%20reported%20in%20August.%20As%20Perplexity%20aims%20to%20eclipse%20Google%20Chrome%2C%20which%20some%20analysts%20estimate%20could%20be%20worth%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%2C%20its%20markups%20aren't%20without%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20the%20advent%20of%20AI%20is%20prompting%20some%20investors%20to%20reevaluate%20what%20a%20%26quot%3Breasonable%26quot%3B%20valuation%20even%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20era%2C%20there's%20a%20belief%20that%20we%20might%20see%20exit%20valuations%20unlike%20any%20we've%20ever%20seen%2C%26quot%3B%20Spain%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20believe%20AI%20is%20going%20to%20be%20transformative%20in%20certain%20industries%2C%20you%20can%20see%20a%20world%20where%20you're%20going%20to%20have%20exits%20that%20are%20just%20abnormally%20large%20relative%20to%20what%20we've%20seen%20historically.%20I%20think%20that's%20the%20right%20conversation%20to%20have%20as%20an%20investor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvestors-cant-keep-up-with-perplexity-nonstop-fundraising-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1761938196000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ee84e55dbc4fd10daad387%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvestors-cant-keep-up-with-perplexity-nonstop-fundraising-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20AI%20search%20engine%20startup%20competing%20with%20Google%20is%20fielding%20investor%20offers%20at%20valuations%20up%20to%20%2450%20billion.%20It's%20making%20some%20VCs%20nervous.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rtorrence%40businessinsider.com%20(Rebecca%20Torrence%2CBen%20Bergman%2CCharles%20Rollet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvestors-cant-keep-up-with-perplexity-nonstop-fundraising-2025-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UGG%20makes%20some%20of%20our%20favorite%20slippers%20ever%2C%20but%20the%20sizing%20can%20be%20wonky%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20here's%20what%20to%20consider%20before%20buying%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22two%20pairs%20of%20UGGs%20side%20by%20side.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6905049d0be9845f2dc582ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmir%20Ismael%2FBackcountry%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhenever%20I%20see%20a%20pair%20of%20sheepskin%20slippers%20or%20boots%2C%20I%20just%20assume%20they're%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nof